  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "body": "This change uses separate http clients/transports in TestValidateToken subtests. Previously parallel subtests of TestValidateToken shared http.DefaultTransport. When one subtest's httptest.Server.Close() ran in t.Cleanup, it called http.DefaultTransport.CloseIdleConnections, which could interrupt connection(s) used in another subtest.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/coder/internal/issues/1514\r\n\r\n",
